	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64587433"><p>Not to mention, they're also far <em>cleaner</em>. Decommissioning of a wind turbine involves finding some creative way to reuse the blades. Decommissioning of a nuclear plant, on the other hand...</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64587433">

</div>
