<div id="comment_status_64587247" class="commentstatus"></div>
<div id="comment_64587247" class="cw">
	<div id="comment_top_64587247" class="commentTop newcomment">
		<div class="title">
			<h4><a id="comment_link_64587247" name="comment_link_64587247" href="//politics.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23371635&amp;cid=64587247" onclick="return D2.setFocusComment(64587247)" >Ask the right questions</a>


		 	<span id="comment_score_64587247" class="score"> (<a href="#" onclick="getModalPrefs('modcommentlog', 'Moderation Comment Log', 64587247); return false"><span class=opt>Score:</span>3</a>)</span></h4>
		</div>
		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~markdavis">markdavis</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~markdavis">( 642305 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_64587247">		
		on Saturday June 29, 2024 @04:29AM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//politics.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=23371635&amp;cid=64587247">#64587247</a>)
		<small> </small>
</span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64587247"><p>&gt;"What's behind these changes?"</p><p>The biggest reasons for the changes are the state of the economy, inflation, and the national debt.  Ask the right questions and you might get answers that reveal this.  Everything is now too expensive, including energy, and people are hurting and want a way out.  A major motivation for renewables is energy independence- something that is very good for security, reducing conflict, and reducing uncertainty/volatility, something everyone is in favor of.  Easy to support in times of plenty, not so motivating when your energy bills (electricity, nat gas, fuel gas) go up over the last several years, (along with everything else), and the interest paid on the ballooning national debt now exceeds defense or medicare spending.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64587247">
